                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18290115-30-victim292 t18290115-30-viclabel139"></join>, and live at Highgate. I lost my coat, on the 13th of December, from the door of an ironmonger's, in <placeName id="t18290115-30-crimeloc140">St. Giles's</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18290115-30-crimeloc140" type="placeName" value="St. Giles's"></interp>
